page.title: 07LIFE IN BRYNNA.
page.content: {A typical weekday of a 11year old {girl 1985. I get up at 8.00a.m.in the morning and go down stairs. I have my break-fast and then get dressed and brush my hair.Then I go to school.I play in the yard till bell goes then we go into assembaly which is religious.After that we go to class and start work.We have 1ST play then we go back in class and work untill dinner bell goes at 12.15pm. We have lunch and go out to play.Then at 1.15 p.m. we go back in class and do art or work .We have anoter bell at 2.30 p.m. untill 2.45 p.m. we do art untill home bell goes at 3.45 p.m. I have my tea, then go out to play till 8.00p.m. then I go to bed at 9.00-10.00p.m.I watch T.V.or the video untill bedtime. By{ { VICTORIA ELLIS.
